{
  "_about": "Interop test vectors. Both Go and Swift cores MUST pass these. RFC vectors are external ground truth (expected codes from the RFC, secrets given as ASCII whose UTF-8 bytes are the raw key). steam/argon2id/vault sections are generated by the Go core and independently cross-verified, then pinned; Swift must match.",
